     C                     KFLD           KKSHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           KKSHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           KKSHN3  2
     C                     MOVEL@SHN1     W1SHN1
     C                     MOVEL@SHN2     W1SHN2
     C                     MOVEL@SHN3     W1SHN3
